{
  "chapter": 93,
  "chapter_summary": "第九十三回\"真帮主\"。芮玮在长江铁网帮夺走简召舞的黑网，震慑帮众。林琼菊当众揭露简召舞冒充芮玮、毒杀黎淑全的罪行。黎淑全死而复生现身，以天罗地网绝技制服简召舞。简怀萱与呼哈娜亦出场指证。简召舞最终认罪，被判押下。林琼菊告知芮玮其父林三寒已被简召舞杀害。欧阳龙年父子带来太阳门战书，芮玮以枯木禅反功震慑欧阳龙年，回信\"战\"字。结尾秦百龄与简召舞越狱逃脱，芮玮推测是齐治平所为，三人将联手对付芮玮。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "恶贼夺去本帮之宝，还不一齐围上！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "芮玮，你叫我哥哥，我自不会害自己的弟弟。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看他还能说些什么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "看在兄弟的分上，我命所有帮众不加害于你，你让出来吧，另外六位女子势必要死在帮众眼前，一泄众人心中的愤怒！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "你承认我这弟弟？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我你面貌相似，自然不假，不用承认，大家也知道了，就这点，谁也不敢伤害于你。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "请问我哥哥姓什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这个自然也姓芮。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "令尊何人？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "先父，先父……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "你不能答，我替你来说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "帮众",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "夫人好！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "令尊天池府……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "闭嘴！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你冒充芮玮骗取黎小姐芳心，婚后又将她害死，其实你不是芮玮，是天池府的简大公子简召舞。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别听她胡言乱语，蛊惑人心，淑全实是病故，有谁不知！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大家有目共睹，淑全实是憔悴病死！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "她生的什么病？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "自老帮主死后，她忧郁成疾，一病亡故。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "贱人，快向兄弟们说明你胡言乱语！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "你谋害了黎小姐，现在又开始谋害我了，可惜你一个也谋害不成！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴南天",
      "listener": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "text": "帮主在上，请受属下一礼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "帮众",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "帮主，帮主！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "帮众",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "帮主没有死，帮主复活啦……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "text": "恭喜黎姑娘未遭贼人谋害，这面黑网应该交给真正的帮主。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "speaker_name": "黎淑全",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我帮弟子听我细诉贼人罪状……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "帮众",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天罗地网！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "speaker_name": "黎淑全",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "恶贼呀！我黎淑全于你有何冤仇，害死我父，又暗害于我……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "speaker_name": "黎淑全",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "先父之死，我本当他病死，却不想你又用同样手法来害我，现在我侥幸不死，才了解先父并非真的病死！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "text": "淑全，你死了之后，我日日以泪洗面，你不要听那贱人瞎说，其中一切我是完全不知，只当床上死的是你，悲痛万分地将你殡葬，谁知奸人暗中捣鬼，把你换去，骗说我要害你，其实我怎会害你，只因奸人要想取代你的位置，施以万毒之计！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "恶贼，到此地步，你还不知忏悔，含血喷人！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天呀，简某做了什么孽，遇上一位心比蛇蝎还毒的女人，他骗我妻子，隐藏起来，教我认为死了，以便下嫁于我，明正言顺的做我妻子。这还罢了，恶毒的女人总是恶毒，现在又不安份，为我生了孩子，又想谋害亲夫了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "简召舞，你一月前就开始在我食物中暗下慢性毒药当我不知道吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "speaker_name": "黎淑全",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "我！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "text": "好淑全，这年来住在什么地方，好教为夫的想念啊！",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "speaker_name": "黎淑全",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "你想我吗？不见得吧！我就住在卧房的夹层内，日日可以偷偷注意你的行动，却不见你有一天想过我嘛！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "text": "我想在心头，你自然看不出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "speaker_name": "黎淑全",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "你谋害林姑娘的举止——落在我的眼内，请问作何解释？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "text": "这因，这因……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "speaker_name": "黎淑全",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "可是发觉林姑娘的不好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对！对！正是有多种不好之处，譬如你之死，我就怀疑是她害的，苦无证据，便思出此条报复之计。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "speaker_name": "黎淑全",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "我带来一人，看你可识得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怀萱、呼哈娜！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "哥哥！哥哥！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "妹妹！",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥，你到底什么时候娶我。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "text": "我……我……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "speaker_name": "黎淑全",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "简召舞，你为要娶这番邦女子是真正毒杀林姑娘的原因！就似前年为了娶林姑娘毒杀我一般，天可怜林姑娘心好，发觉你的阴谋，眼看我快要死了，换了一具貌似我的尸首，把我藏起，暗暗服侍我。这年来我还能够苟延残喘，完全靠她多方寻觅各种解毒之药，谁知你手段毒辣，所下的慢性毒，竟是天下奇毒，未能完全解去，迄今未能康复如前！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我根本不识那番邦女子！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "大哥，你还是认罪吧，自那日我与呼哈娜来投靠你，呼哈娜以为你是芮玮，我却立时看出你是我的哥哥，虽然你尽量装是芮玮，但你笑容永远学不像芮玮！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "你看上呼哈娜姐，将我俩安置另处，我便知你的用意，吩咐呼哈娜小心提防，是我教她，非明正言顺娶过去不可，谁知为此竟害了林姑娘，却非我所料想到的！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "好个亲妹妹，伙同外人算计哥哥来了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "实在我不应再喊你哥哥了，你害死母亲，二哥，我岂能再认你，你……你的行为……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的行为纯是自卫，我不杀你母亲、兄弟，便要将被他们害死！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "speaker_name": "黎淑全",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "简召舞，你当私藏两位女人便无人知道吗？要知天下事除非已莫为，鲜有不被人知者。怀萱妹本与我有过一面之识，和她相见才确知你是天池府的简召舞，并非掌剑飞芮问夫的儿子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "speaker_name": "黎淑全",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "亏怀萱妹大义凛然，共思揭你罪状之计，但因你势力过于雄厚，不敢轻举妄动，今天固长老、单长老、简长老已去，你失了得力的翅膀，正好来细细一算！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "算又怎地，不算又怎地，大不了一死而已，但我一死，你只做个苦守闺寂的活寡妇了，还有我的现任妻子，你还好，尚有位咱们的女儿伴你！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "帮众",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快杀了这恶贼替老帮主报仇。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "帮众",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "五马分尸或是凌迟，决不让这种恶贼死得痛快！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "简召舞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的大帮主，我的活寡妇，快下命吧，别让大家等得慌！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "text": "姐姐，你……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "speaker_name": "黎淑全",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "押下去！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "text": "姐姐处置他……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "speaker_name": "黎淑全",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也做不得十分的主，此间事最大功臣是芮公子。咱们还是请问芮公子意见如何？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我无意见。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你还想找我父亲报仇吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你大概还不知先父已经去世将近一年了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "令尊如何去世的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "仇家杀死！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "哪一个仇家？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "很可惜仇家不是你本人吗？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "最近我实下决心，手刃林堡主替父亲报仇！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "简召舞杀的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "正是那个前世的冤家！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "他为何要杀林堡主？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "简召舞此人记仇心最重，只因那年黑堡天地人三魔冒犯了天池府，他便存下报仇的心理。去年他得到固鹏三长老加入后，自以为从此不可一世，以前的仇家一一寻思报复。一天他带齐治平去趟山西，跟我说拜访家父。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "回来后我问他家父身体可好，他说好得紧呀！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我见他说话神态有异，暗中追问齐治平，齐治平经不起我一再追问，漏出家父被他杀死的真相。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_bo",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳波",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这便是月形门弟子嘛！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "月形门弟子何在？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "欧阳前辈，别来无恙？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "小子，咱们又相会了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "月形门弟子死绝了吗？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "前辈口齿为何如此不净！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "莫非月形门弟子与你相熟？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "在下即是月形门弟子！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你也配！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "前辈寻月形门弟子有何贵事？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "叫月形门弟子出来听话。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "此地即我一人是月形门弟子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我试试你到底有多重斤量自称月形门弟子！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "前辈可是吃到了葫芦岛底的怪鲜？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你能吃到，我当然也能吃到！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "难怪你要向我一试手劲了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "握手有出左掌之理吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "右掌也行。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "要不要试换左手，只是一握左手，你欧阳龙年要吃大亏，怕的话，最好不试。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我有一信面交月形门掌门。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "交给我一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "回信如何？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "战！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "speaker_name": "黎淑全",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "text": "在下一个请求。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "speaker_name": "黎淑全",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "什么请求尽管说，不用客气。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "text": "我有两件事请问泰百龄，第一件……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "speaker_name": "黎淑全",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你在怀疑发信人是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "speaker_name": "黎淑全",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "太阳掌门人在此，还有谁发此傲气高于纸上的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "text": "所以我想一问秦百龄，另一件事，我有一子落在他手中要向他索回。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "speaker_name": "黎淑全",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "令子何名？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "text": "纪野。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "speaker_name": "黎淑全",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我非月形门弟子，秦百龄实不用留在我处，交你带去，任你处置吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "text": "多谢！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "帮众",
      "listener": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "text": "牢……牢……中犯人丢了……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "speaker_name": "黎淑全",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "丢了谁？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "帮众",
      "listener": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "text": "太阳掌门人秦百龄。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "帮众",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "speaker_name": "黎淑全",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有谁？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是简召舞？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "speaker_name": "黎淑全",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁个大胆放的？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "帮众",
      "listener": "char_li_shu_quan",
      "text": "不，不知道。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 564,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "齐治平齐教师在不在。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "帮众",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这……这大半天没见着他的人影。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 93,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    },
